  "instructions": [
    "Heat 2 tablespoons of olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the finely chopped onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the peppercorns and paprika, and cook for 30 seconds.",
    "Add the carnaroli-rice and cook, stirring constantly, for 2 minutes.",
    "Add 1 cup of water to the skillet and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and cook for 12 minutes or until the rice is tender and fluffy.",
    "Stir in the freshly squeezed lemon juice and chopped parsley.",
    "Transfer the pilaf to a serving platter and garnish with cucumber slices.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
